For initial setup, run the following commands from inside the project's root directory:

sudo npm update -g cordova

mkdir {hooks,merges,platforms,plugins}

cordova platform add ios

cp icons_backup/* platforms/ios/MyWarbands/Resources/icons/ && cp splash_backup/* platforms/ios/MyWarbands/Resources/splash/

cordova plugins add cordova-plugin-inappbrowser cordova-plugin-file cordova-plugin-file-transfer com.ben2.cordova.keyboard https://github.com/ohh2ahh/AppAvailability.git de.appplant.cordova.plugin.hidden-statusbar-overlay cordova-plugin-dialogs https://github.com/steve-jansen/cordova-ios-emailcomposer com.disusered.open

cordova build